{"tid":1461044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬炒] 青年攬炒？ 其實唔係，係大勝。 有手有腳有頭腦 vs 廢老","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:44:28.000Z","uid":771,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"435a2861bc5c8b1824096e06d9d9207527d1e4dd","tid":1461044,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"今時今日，廢老零工作能力渣住物業壓炸青年勞動成果<br />\n<br />\n如果香港經濟爆煲，舖冇人租，樓冇人買<br />\n<br />\n每個人赤婐婐就係靠自己既手腳頭腦生存<br />\n<br />\n資本效應大大減低<br />\n<br />\n咁，係呢個情況底下，係年青人有競爭力，定係d 廢老有？<br />\n<br />\n唔洗諗，攬炒之下，我地大勝！"},{"pid":"4464dd02531c9489bb0ef48b149ff4260b541aab","tid":1461044,"uid":771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"唔會怕攬炒，我有手有腳，起間木屋比自己住都仲得<br />\n<br />\n洗閪怕你d 廢老"},{"pid":"1cbfaa1a313eb8d9fc7aaf2891189f455366c074","tid":1461044,"uid":245484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"人一想留一手就好撚易輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒之後既事，攬炒左之後再講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4432d9c77e4cab5b9157afaa641693fc7391d733","tid":1461044,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"你口中既廢老幾間屋租比你班弱智住"},{"pid":"284faf229df61c7918df5eb439a4fe8e72c06852","tid":1461044,"uid":771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4432d9c77e4cab5b9157afaa641693fc7391d733","tid":1461044,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"你口中既廢老幾間屋租比你班弱智住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"經濟差果時，冇人租仲要蝕維修保養管理費"},{"pid":"cee1fda681ab27bffeeee82f0f3a9e7038314dfd","tid":1461044,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"284faf229df61c7918df5eb439a4fe8e72c06852","tid":1461044,"uid":771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4432d9c77e4cab5b9157afaa641693fc7391d733","tid":1461044,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":4